---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout 
	title="ELRS Mobile | Flash & Configure ExpressLRS from your Phone" 
	description="Flash and configure ExpressLRS receivers and transmitters directly from your iOS or Android device. 100% offline flashing, no PC or cables required."
>
	<main class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-4">
		<section class="text-center py-16 md:py-32">
			<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-7xl font-black leading-tight md:leading-[1.1] mb-6 md:mb-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-white via-white to-primary bg-clip-text text-transparent break-words">
				The Field-Ready ExpressLRS Tool. No Laptop Required.
			</h1>
			<p class="text-lg md:text-2xl text-text-muted max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 md:mb-12">
				Flash V3.x and V4.x Firmware via Wi-Fi directly from your iOS or Android device.
			</p>
			
			<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-center items-center gap-4 md:gap-6 mb-8">
				<a
					href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=io.datarx.elrsmobile"
					class="w-full md:w-auto px-8 py-3.5 rounded-xl font-bold text-base md:text-lg transition-all hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:brightness-110 text-center bg-primary text-background no-underline"
					onclick="gtag('event', 'app_download_click', { 'store': 'google_play' });"
				>Get it on Google Play</a>
				<a
					href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/elrs-mobile/id6760490014"
					class="w-full md:w-auto px-8 py-3.5 rounded-xl font-bold text-base md:text-lg transition-all hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:brightness-110 text-center bg-primary text-background no-underline"
					onclick="gtag('event', 'app_download_click', { 'store': 'apple_app_store' });"
				>Download on App Store</a>
			</div>

			<div class="flex justify-center items-center gap-3 md:gap-4 text-text-muted text-sm md:text-base">
				<a href="/user_guide" class="text-inherit no-underline transition-colors hover:text-primary">Documentation</a>
				<span class="opacity-30">|</span>
				<a
					href="https://github.com/wbhinton/ELRS-Mobile"
					class="text-inherit no-underline transition-colors hover:text-primary"
				>Project GitHub</a>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id="use-cases" class="py-12 md:py-20">
			<div class="text-center mb-10 md:mb-16">
				<h2 class="text-2xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-3 md:mb-4 tracking-tight">Why ELRS Mobile?</h2>
				<p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-text-muted max-w-2xl mx-auto">Real-world solutions for the field and the bench.</p>
			</div>
			
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 md:gap-8">
				<div class="bg-surface/40 backdrop-blur-md rounded-2xl border border-primary/10 p-6 md:p-10 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-primary/30 hover:shadow-[0_20px_40px_rgba(0,191,165,0.07)] flex flex-col gap-4">
					<div class="flex justify-between items-start gap-4">
						<span class="text-[0.7rem] font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wider px-2.5 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-primary/10 text-primary">Problem</span>
						<h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold">The "Dead Zone" Mismatch</h3>
					</div>
					<p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed text-sm md:text-base grow">
						You're at a remote bando and realize your TX is on v4.0 but your RX is on v3.3. No cell service, no laptop, and no way to reach the Web Flasher.
					</p>
					<div class="p-5 md:p-6 bg-primary/5 rounded-xl border-l-[3px] border-primary text-sm md:text-base">
						<strong class="block text-primary mb-1">The Fix:</strong> Open the app, select your cached target, and flash via Wi-Fi. Back in the air in under 60 seconds—zero bars required.
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-surface/40 backdrop-blur-md rounded-2xl border border-primary/10 p-6 md:p-10 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-primary/30 hover:shadow-[0_20px_40px_rgba(0,191,165,0.07)] flex flex-col gap-4">
					<div class="flex justify-between items-start gap-4">
						<span class="text-[0.7rem] font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wider px-2.5 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-primary/10 text-primary">Updates</span>
						<h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold">Mass Configuration</h3>
					</div>
					<p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed text-sm md:text-base grow">
						Changed your home Wi-Fi password or SSID? Bringing ten aircraft to your PC just to update a text string is a massive chore.
					</p>
					<div class="p-5 md:p-6 bg-primary/5 rounded-xl border-l-[3px] border-primary text-sm md:text-base">
						<strong class="block text-primary mb-1">The Fix:</strong> Bring your phone to the fleet. Connect to each quad's AP and update network settings or binding phrases natively and instantly.
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 md:gap-8 py-12 md:py-20">
			<div class="bg-surface/40 backdrop-blur-md rounded-2xl border border-primary/10 p-6 md:p-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-primary/30 hover:shadow-[0_20px_40px_rgba(0,191,165,0.07)] flex flex-col gap-3">
				<h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-primary">⚡ Blazing Fast</h3>
				<p class="text-text-muted text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">Flash from local cache instead of waiting for web downloads or cloud compiles.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="bg-surface/40 backdrop-blur-md rounded-2xl border border-primary/10 p-6 md:p-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-primary/30 hover:shadow-[0_20px_40px_rgba(0,191,165,0.07)] flex flex-col gap-3">
				<h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-primary">📡 Reliable Anywhere</h3>
				<p class="text-text-muted text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">Engineered for resilience. Direct OTA flashing ensures stable connections even in remote areas.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="bg-surface/40 backdrop-blur-md rounded-2xl border border-primary/10 p-6 md:p-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-primary/30 hover:shadow-[0_20px_40px_rgba(0,191,165,0.07)] flex flex-col gap-3">
				<h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-primary">🛠 Unified Flow</h3>
				<p class="text-text-muted text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">One interface for all hardware. Automatically patches firmware with your config before flashing.</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="demo py-12 md:py-20 text-center">
			<div class="mb-10 md:mb-16">
				<h2 class="text-2xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-3 md:mb-4 tracking-tight">See it in Action</h2>
				<p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-text-muted max-w-2xl mx-auto">Quick OTA flashing from local cache.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="flex justify-center py-4">
				<div class="w-full max-w-[300px] aspect-[9/18.5] bg-black border-[10px] border-[#1a1a1a] rounded-[36px] relative overflow-hidden shadow-[0_30px_60px_rgba(0,0,0,0.6)] mx-auto after:content-[''] after:absolute after:top-0 after:left-1/2 after:-translate-x-1/2 after:w-[120px] after:h-[24px] after:bg-[#1a1a1a] after:rounded-b-xl">
					<iframe
						width="100%"
						height="100%"
						src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/v1gV7t4i-dA"
						title="ELRS Mobile Flashing Demo"
						frameborder="0"
						allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
						allowfullscreen
					>
					</iframe>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id="installation" class="py-12 md:py-20">
			<div class="text-center mb-10 md:mb-16">
				<h2 class="text-2xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-3 md:mb-4 tracking-tight">Get Started</h2>
				<p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-text-muted max-w-2xl mx-auto">Choose your platform and join the flight.</p>
			</div>
			
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 md:gap-6 mb-8 md:mb-12">
				<a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=io.datarx.elrsmobile" class="flex items-center gap-4 md:gap-6 p-5 md:p-6 bg-surface border border-white/5 rounded-2xl no-underline text-white transition-all hover:border-primary hover:bg-primary/[0.03] hover:-translate-y-1">
					<div class="text-primary">
						<svg class="w-9 h-9 md:w-12 md:h-12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M17.523 15.3414L20.355 13.706C21.215 13.209 21.215 11.961 20.355 11.464L17.523 9.82944L14.771 12.5834L17.523 15.3414ZM13.883 13.4724L16.635 16.2234L5.656 22.564C5.071 22.902 4.331 22.795 3.865 22.28L13.883 13.4724ZM3.535 20.916L12.997 12.5844L3.535 4.25144C3.195 4.41444 3 4.76744 3 5.16644V20.0014C3 20.4 3.195 20.7534 3.535 20.916ZM13.883 11.6964L3.865 2.88844C4.331 2.37344 5.071 2.26644 5.656 2.60444L16.635 8.94544L13.883 11.6964Z"></path></svg>
					</div>
					<div class="store-info">
						<h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold m-0">Google Play</h3>
						<span class="text-[0.7rem] font-extrabold text-primary uppercase bg-primary/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">Production</span>
					</div>
				</a>
				<a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/elrs-mobile/id6760490014" class="flex items-center gap-4 md:gap-6 p-5 md:p-6 bg-surface border border-white/5 rounded-2xl no-underline text-white transition-all hover:border-primary hover:bg-primary/[0.03] hover:-translate-y-1">
					<div class="text-primary">
						<svg class="w-9 h-9 md:w-12 md:h-12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M17.05 20.28c-.96.95-2.06 1.92-3.4 1.92s-1.8-.84-3.37-.84-2.1.84-3.41.84c-1.28 0-2.43-1.02-3.41-2.45-2.17-3.17-3.26-7.44-1.17-10.73 1-1.5 2.51-2.48 4.14-2.48 1.4 0 2.4 1.05 3.4 1.05s2.2-.9 3.55-.9c1.1 0 2.45.6 3.45 1.7-2.7 1.6-2.2 5.3 0 6.6-.7 1.8-1.7 3.6-2.94 5.16zM13 2c0 1.5-1.26 3.1-2.9 3.1-.15-1.9 1.4-3.5 2.9-3.5z"></path></svg>
					</div>
					<div class="store-info">
						<h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold m-0">App Store</h3>
						<span class="text-[0.7rem] font-extrabold text-primary uppercase bg-primary/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">Production</span>
					</div>
				</a>
			</div>

			<div class="text-center p-8 md:p-12 bg-surface/30 backdrop-blur-md rounded-[24px] md:rounded-[32px] border border-white/5 shadow-2xl">
				<h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-2 tracking-tight">Advanced Installation</h3>
				<p class="text-text-muted text-sm md:text-base">Direct downloads and source code for power users.</p>
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 md:gap-6 mt-6 md:mt-8">
					<a href="https://github.com/OpenHub-Store/Github-Store" class="bg-white/5 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 p-5 md:p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-primary/50 hover:bg-white/10 text-left no-underline group">
						<h4 class="text-white font-bold mb-1 transition-colors group-hover:text-primary">GitHub Store</h4>
						<p class="text-text-muted text-sm m-0">Download via OpenHub Store</p>
					</a>
					<a href="https://github.com/wbhinton/ELRS-Mobile/releases" class="bg-white/5 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 p-5 md:p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-primary/50 hover:bg-white/10 text-left no-underline group">
						<h4 class="text-white font-bold mb-1 transition-colors group-hover:text-primary">Android APK</h4>
						<p class="text-text-muted text-sm m-0">Sideload via GitHub Releases</p>
					</a>
					<a href="https://github.com/wbhinton/ELRS-Mobile" class="bg-white/5 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 p-5 md:p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-primary/50 hover:bg-white/10 text-left no-underline group">
						<h4 class="text-white font-bold mb-1 transition-colors group-hover:text-primary">Source Code</h4>
						<p class="text-text-muted text-sm m-0">View on GitHub</p>
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id="hardware" class="py-12 md:py-20">
			<div class="text-center mb-10 md:mb-16">
				<h2 class="text-2xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-3 md:mb-4 tracking-tight">Compatibility</h2>
				<p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-text-muted max-w-2xl mx-auto">Broad support for the ExpressLRS ecosystem.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 md:gap-8 mb-6 md:mb-8">
				<div class="bg-surface/30 backdrop-blur-md rounded-2xl border border-white/5 p-6 md:p-8 shadow-xl">
					<h4 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-6 text-primary tracking-tight">Supported Chipsets</h4>
					<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
						<span class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-primary/10 border border-primary/20 text-primary text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">ESP8285</span>
						<span class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-primary/10 border border-primary/20 text-primary text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">ESP32</span>
						<span class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-primary/10 border border-primary/20 text-primary text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">ESP32-C3</span>
						<span class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-primary/10 border border-primary/20 text-primary text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">ESP32-S3</span>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="bg-surface/30 backdrop-blur-md rounded-2xl border border-white/5 p-6 md:p-8 shadow-xl">
					<h4 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-6 text-primary tracking-tight">Tested Hardware</h4>
					<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
						<span class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-white/90 text-xs font-medium italic">RadioMaster XR Series</span>
						<span class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-white/90 text-xs font-medium italic">BetaFPV SuperP</span>
						<span class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-white/90 text-xs font-medium italic">HappyModel ES900 / EP</span>
						<span class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-white/90 text-xs font-medium italic">RadioMaster Nomad / Pocket</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<div class="text-center py-8 md:py-16 border-t border-white/5">
			<p class="text-sm md:text-base">Need help? Visit the <a href="/user_guide" class="text-primary font-bold no-underline hover:underline">User Guide</a>.</p>
		</div>

		<footer class="text-center pb-16 md:pb-20 text-text-muted text-[0.85rem]">
			<p>&copy; 2026 Weston Hinton. Distributed under the GNU GPL v3.</p>
			<div class="text-[0.7rem] max-w-3xl mx-auto my-6 opacity-60 leading-relaxed">
				ExpressLRS™ is a trademark of ExpressLRS LLC. ELRS Mobile is an independent FOSS project and is not affiliated with or endorsed by ExpressLRS LLC.
			</div>
			<div class="mt-6 px-6 py-3 bg-primary/5 rounded-full inline-block">
				Support the project: <a href="https://opencollective.com/expresslrs/donate" class="text-primary font-bold no-underline hover:underline ml-2">Donate to ExpressLRS</a>
			</div>
		</footer>
	</main>
</Layout>

<script>
	declare global {
		interface Window {
			gtag: (command: string, action: string, params?: object) => void;
		}
	}

	document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
		const playStoreLinks = document.querySelectorAll('a[href*="play.google.com/store/apps/details"]');
		const appleAppStoreLinks = document.querySelectorAll('a[href*="apps.apple.com"]');

		playStoreLinks.forEach(link => {
			link.addEventListener('click', () => {
				if (typeof window.gtag === 'function') {
					window.gtag('event', 'app_download_click', {
						'store': 'google_play',
						'event_category': 'App Install',
						'event_label': 'Play Store Link'
					});
				}
			});
		});

		appleAppStoreLinks.forEach(link => {
			link.addEventListener('click', () => {
				if (typeof window.gtag === 'function') {
					window.gtag('event', 'app_download_click', {
						'store': 'apple_app_store',
						'event_category': 'App Install',
						'event_label': 'App Store Link'
					});
				}
			});
		});
	});
</script>
